snippet.description: Celebrity Wire is the ultimate in entertainment news from around the world. We bring you the best and hottest celebrity updates, daily news, hollywood red carpet interviews, chats with the hottest superstars and much more. Make sure to come back every day to not miss out on the latest gossip and fashion trends on Celebrity Wire.
